TITLE: Implementing Dark Mode in Bulma with CSS
DESCRIPTION: CSS implementation showing how Bulma defines its dark theme, combining media queries for user preferences with data attributes and classes for manual control.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/docs/documentation/features/dark-mode.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
```
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    /* Update CSS variables */
  }
}

[data-theme=dark],
.theme-dark {
  /* Update CSS variables */
}
```

