TITLE: Demonstrating CSS Variable Scope in Bulma
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how CSS variables can be defined at different scopes, with component-level variables overriding global ones. This example shows a global medium size being overridden in the button component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/docs/documentation/features/css-variables.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
