TITLE: Newsletter Layout Example with Automatic Spacing in Bulma
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet demonstrates a newsletter layout with Bulma components where the automatic spacing between elements (notification, table, pagination) creates a visually balanced design with 1.5rem margins between components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/docs/_posts/2021-01-23-the-block-probably-bulmas-most-important-feature.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

