TITLE: Installing Bulma via Bower
DESCRIPTION: Command to install Bulma CSS framework using Bower package manager
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
bower install bulma
```

