TITLE: Displaying File and Diff Statistics in HTML
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to display file and diff statistics using HTML figure and img elements. It visualizes the scope of changes made during the website redesign.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/docs/_posts/2018-04-13-website-redesign.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<figure>
  <img src="{{ site.url }}/images/blog/v7/files.png" alt="files" width="312" height="37">
  <br>
  <img src="{{ site.url }}/images/blog/v7/diff.png" alt="diff" width="167" height="38">
</figure>
```

