TITLE: Defining Markdown Frontmatter for Bulma Version Access Post
DESCRIPTION: This markdown frontmatter defines metadata for a blog post about accessing previous Bulma versions. It includes layout, title, introduction, and other relevant information for the post.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/blob/main/docs/_posts/2017-07-24-access-previous-bulma-versions.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
---
layout: post
title: "Access previous Bulma versions"
introduction: "It is now possible to **access previous versions** of Bulma"
long_introduction: "It is now possible to **access previous versions** of Bulma. Just head towards: [http://versions.bulma.io/](http://versions.bulma.io/)"
color: "primary"
name: "Versions"
icon: "undo"
---
```

